title: Desserts 365 Recipes - A Different Dish For Every Day.pdf Gooner
description: A great collection of recipes for every day of the year, covering a fantastic selection of delicious desserts. This is an ideal book for today's busy lifestyle with a whole range of ideas for every occasion. Desserts is perfect for both the experienced cook and beginners looking for easy to follow recipes that are simple to cook and a treat to eat.
